\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鞭"},{"pid":"6310db1662a020d710894927b435bf30c5658be2","tid":1751641,"uid":106252,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:53:02.000Z","msg":"其實佢都唔係咩好人"},{"pid":"bbd5d98da4713b19c4e19d23eab298d181fd65ac","tid":1751641,"uid":225100,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:53:44.000Z","msg":"希望泛民當選人可以考慮下沈教授嘅建議<br />\n唔係嘅話 總有一日會分裂<br />\n//<br />\n全體非建制派參選人，其實應該及早簽署一個簡單約章，一切理念那些虛的東西一概不必，只有一個條款：<span style=\"color: gold;\">當選後，願意每月捐出五千元，共同成立一個基金</span>。基金並非由這些區議員管理，而是委任一些勇武派、本土派相對信任（或起碼接受）的社會賢達，或被剝奪選舉權的代表共同管理，例如本土論述權威孔誥烽教授、練乙崢教授、陳雲博士、被高調DQ的黃之鋒、已經身在獄中的梁天琦等，負責營運這個支援前線的基金，特別註明支援那些因為參加運動而被控告、坐牢、出走的前線朋友。假如非建制派得到200席，這就是每月100萬、一年1200萬、三年3600萬，再找一些同情運動的中產眾籌一個1:1的matching fund，一場選舉，就可以成立多一個7200萬元的基金，也就是另一個「612基金」。這不能解決所有問題，但可以慢慢建構「和勇命運共同體」，這其實是雙方都需要的。<br />\n//<br />\n沈旭暉：大考驗・大戰略：區議會選舉後的分裂與團結<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1750945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1750945</a>"},{"pid":"8208b43097b2d56a0ce5496bb62026eed6b30f14","tid":1751641,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e291ecfe346c39bb741fce734300ac052c99be2c","tid":1751641,"uid":2772,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:51:43.000Z","msg":"邊個住嗰區選個建制出黎<br />\n應該要為自己感到羞恥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:54:01.000Z","msg":"垃圾地區照妖鏡"},{"pid":"f843995bbaf10cf246f50733d01d91550be99668","tid":1751641,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:54:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咪撚做休息撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n投完票，贏輸都好，我地有新野做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">文宣方向：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 有得一人一票，社會氣氛好左幾多？而且大家都相信投票，年青人到長者教出黎投，所以應該一人一票選特首。<br />\n<br />\n2.我地要將種票、票多過投票人、送禮各種唔公平現象比英美兩國知。<br />\n<br />\n3. Poly手足被困多日，要求警察撤退。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBe water be humble </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n‪Hi Solomon,today&rsquo;s Election rate are near to 2 Million people, does it means that, election (including Chief executive) are believed and suitable in Hong Kong?‬"},{"pid":"1c453b0a500627756b28d0bf69669da76eb45dce","tid":1751641,"uid":261505,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:54:29.000Z","msg":"條友咩都無做空降落去空叫口號就想贏 當人戇鳩<br />\n民建聯係柒 但至少d廢老都叫有野拎下 有訴求會聽下<br />\n你係普通人會點揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c107d4cac2de5c305d0ddcbe03cce9e2ab61df","tid":1751641,"uid":153,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:54:52.000Z","msg":"負評多到 d人含撚含到吞劍咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人血饅頭佼佼者都唔識學人講政治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"655832b9350321ec68cfa8a06f73952f6f098f03","tid":1751641,"uid":7940,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:55:12.000Z","msg":"傻鳩毛"},{"pid":"209195c9cfd68842a749fe8fdbb2ca7ab59aeb80","tid":1751641,"uid":76776,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:56:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b40f82e01d0bbbbd4d2c981761699c8f45ebbc8c","tid":1751641,"uid":235890,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24